24/02/2006
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Travel by Macedonian citizens to Estonia will be easier in the future, as Estonia has simplified procedures for obtaining visas and decided to grant them free of charge. Visiting Skopje on Thursday (23 February) Estonian Foreign Minister Urmas Paet also pledged that Tallinn would share its experience regarding EU accession. (MIA, Makfax - 23/02/06) 
